title: Team Matadors end on top at Texas Tech Spring Game - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: Team Matadors end on top at Texas Tech Spring Game - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: Rayshad Williams picked off the second pass of the Texas Tech Spring Game and raced 38 yards into the end zone, spring boarding Team Matadors to a 24-6 victory over Team Red Raiders Saturday at Jones AT&T Stadium.
